    "answer": "1. Native Timeout: Set the 'Timeout' property on the pipeline settings (under General). For example, set it to `02:00:00` (2 hours). If the pipeline runs longer, the ADF service automatically cancels the run, throwing a timeout error.\n\n2. Activity Timeout: Alternatively, set timeouts on long-running individual activities (like Copy or Web) to ensure they terminate quickly if they hang, preventing runaway costs without needing custom API termination scripts.",
